{"tid":1576954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］穆迪點解降評級去「負面」 林鄭先係全港最強攪抄巴","createTime":"2019-09-17T12:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T14:32:04.000Z","uid":304737,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c9c28c5801a20549f49e28d523186b02c28b1a","tid":1576954,"uid":304737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">之前穆迪已經講過 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港示威者係起到制衡政府嘅作用</span></strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong> 對香港經濟環境唔單止冇害 <span style=\"color: red;\">反正係香港經濟上獨立性嘅展現 係好事黎架</span></strong></span> </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「至於穆迪，則曾經發表評論，指抗議活動是香港制衡政府的手段之一，若此制衡能力有被削弱的迹象，將對香港的信貸評級產生負面影響」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁點降而家評級展望降低呀？點解負面呀？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>咪因為香港人連抗議嘅自由都冇埋</strong></span> </span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">本來制度內靠立會靠法治監察政府 偏偏政府不斷破壞香港三權分立變成</strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>人治</strong></span> <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"></span><br />\n而係建制外市民連遊行集會嘅人權都被剝削 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>依個政權已經冇枉管 咁邊個敢投資呀？ <br />\n評級咪跌囉</strong></span></span></span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><br />\n所以而家降級<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>唔係因為示威</strong></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>而係因為港府唔解決問題 <br />\n反而用盡暴力手段同示威者持續對峙<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n穆迪話係 「削弱香港自行管治及司法的可預期性」同時「加速港府與中國聯繫」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>本來香港有得發達嘅重要因素係高度自治同一國兩制</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔係你同中国有咩分別呀 點解外資唔直接上去搵錢呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劏房波想點唔認都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地嘅事實根據就係香港一直良好嘅營商環境俾依個政府斷送哂 你破壞哂咪冇錢賺囉</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你咁鍾意中港融合丫嘛 你咪跟埋中国評級囉好冇</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>所以搞亂香港嘅唔係提出問題嘅人 而係唔解決問題嘅人<br />\n所以我宣佈全香港最大嘅攪抄巴係林鄭政府</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d844e2d0d43b6419e5e9e78ac43450149dd1e4","tid":1576954,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"正名 香港保衛戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdbc5fd8990966fe8b54f79c4852ae46f014123","tid":1